d its follow-up detailsReal-time (same day)Preparation of beneficiary list (maker)1st of every monthChecking of beneficiary details (checker)3rd of every monthApproval of beneficiary list with details (approver)5th of every monthProcessing of payments7th of every monthDocuments Required for Nikshay Poshan Yojana ApplicationHere is the complete list of documents necessary for Nikshay Poshan Yojana application form:-Doctor\u2019s certificate \u2013 As only TB patients will be able to apply for this scheme, it is mandatory for them to submit necessary medical papers. These papers will support the claim of patients.Application form \u2013 Apart from medical certificates, patients need submit their application forms as well. The form will offer respective authority members details about patients.For more details , read Nikshay Poshan Yojana PDF NotificationNeed for Nikshay Poshan Yojana PortalThe central govt. has created Nikshay Poshan Yojana Portal for the following purposes:-Creating a platform for TB treatment \u2013 This portal will enable govt. to monitor TB patients and offer them assistance so that they can get the upper hand on the disease.Recording details of TB patients \u2013 The concerned dept. will take necessary steps to record data of all patients who make Nikshay Poshan Yojana Enrollment.Offering financial assistance \u2013 All TB patients will receive Rs. 500 on a monthly basis.Frequency of payment \u2013 The central govt. will provide financial assistance to the patients each month. This grant will be continued till the patients get well.Total beneficiaries \u2013 The total number of patients enrolled under Nikshay Poshan scheme has reached 13 lakh.Funds Transfer \u2013 All TB patients will receive their financial grant directly in their active bank accounts, which have been linked with Aadhar Cards. The funds will be transferred via Direct Benefit Transfer or DBT.The implementation of the special Nikshay medical scheme will offer help to the TB patients which would be done under the National Health Mission.References\u2014 Nikshay Poshan Yojana (Videos, Tweets & Posters) Click Here To Download \u2014 For more details, visit the official website at https://nikshay.in/  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: nikshay.in  at  "}